and the first season where we're currently in the middle of that.

7
00:00:26,862 --> 00:00:29,662
I would like to open with one short slide about myself,

8
00:00:30,082 --> 00:00:31,042
that you know who's talking.

9
00:00:31,463 --> 00:00:33,903
And I like defining myself actually more with my games

10
00:00:34,603 --> 00:00:35,443
than with anything else.

11
00:00:36,024 --> 00:00:39,664
I started rather early in 1987 on the Commodore 64.

12
