18
00:00:55,248 --> 00:00:56,208
I was there for four years.

19
00:00:57,146 --> 00:00:59,987
And now I'm, for six and a half years, I'm with Square Enix,

20
00:01:00,687 --> 00:01:03,589
and I'm now a studio head at Iron Interactive in Copenhagen,

21
00:01:03,989 --> 00:01:06,990
and we are known for many games like Minion Ninjas,

22
00:01:07,010 --> 00:01:09,031
Freedom Fighters, the Kane and Lynch series,

23
00:01:09,531 --> 00:01:11,512
but most of all for Hitman,

24
00:01:12,032 --> 00:01:13,773
and that's what I want to talk about today.

25
00:01:14,793 --> 00:01:18,454
So the main points, I will try to keep it concise

26
00:01:19,235 --> 00:01:20,575
because it is a lot to take in.

27
00:01:21,570 --> 00:01:24,352
and I want you to get something out of this presentation.

28
