So I will give you a short overview of Hitman,

29
00:01:28,174 --> 00:01:29,655
what the brand is, what the game is,

30
00:01:30,035 --> 00:01:31,536
because that is the foundation,

31
00:01:31,616 --> 00:01:33,037
the baseline that we started with,

32
00:01:33,557 --> 00:01:35,138
and that's why that is relevant to understand.

33
