The majority of this talk today will be about

34
00:01:38,119 --> 00:01:41,081
what we call internally Hitman 2016,

35
00:01:41,941 --> 00:01:43,682
because it's the sixth game in the series,

36
00:01:44,523 --> 00:01:48,165
but it's the first game that we just called plain Hitman.

37
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:51,640
and lacking a subtitle, we dubbed it 2016.

38
